<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Returns & Refund Policy - AutoBids Seller</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #007bff;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #007bff;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .header p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .effective-date {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff, #0056b3);
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .policy-section {
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            padding: 25px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-left: 5px solid #007bff;
        }

        .policy-section h2 {
            color: #007bff;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .policy-section h2:before {
            content: "▶";
            margin-right: 10px;
            color: #28a745;
        }

        .highlight-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e3f2fd, #bbdefb);
            border: 2px solid #2196f3;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .highlight-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0d47a1;
        }

        .highlight-item:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .highlight-item:before {
            content: "✓";
            background: #28a745;
            color: white;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-right: 12px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .warning-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3cd, #ffeaa7);
            border: 2px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .warning-box h3 {
            color: #856404;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            padding-left: 25px;
            position: relative;
        }

        li:before {
            content: "•";
            color: #007bff;
            font-weight: bold;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .process-steps {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }

        .process-steps ol {
            list-style: none;
            counter-reset: step-counter;
        }

        .process-steps ol li {
            counter-increment: step-counter;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #007bff;
        }

        .process-steps ol li:before {
            content: counter(step-counter);
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            width: 25px;
            height: 25px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-right: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .contact-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745, #20c997);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .contact-box h3 {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }

        .contact-info {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .contact-item {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .contact-item strong {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .timeframe {
            background: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 12px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .cost-info {
            background: #dc3545;
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 12px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                margin: 10px;
                padding: 15px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            
            .contact-info {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            
            .policy-section {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Returns & Refund Policy</h1>
            <p>AutoBids Seller - Used & Refurbished Engine Specialists</p>
            <div class="effective-date">Effective Date: August 19, 2025</div>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
            <h2>Return Window</h2>
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <span class="timeframe">7 days</span> Return requests must be submitted within 7 days of delivery
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <span class="timeframe">14 days</span> Approved returns must be shipped back within 14 days after authorization
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
            <h2>Cost of Return</h2>
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <span class="cost-info">Customer pays return shipping</span> Return shipping costs are the responsibility of the customer unless the item was damaged, defective, or incorrectly shipped by AutoBids
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <span class="cost-info">Restocking fee: 25%</span> A restocking fee of twenty-five percent (25%) applies to all approved returns
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
            <h2>Eligible Return Items</h2>
            <div class="warning-box">
                <h3>⚠️ Returns Accepted for Defective Products Only</h3>
                <p><strong>Due to the used/refurbished nature of our engines, we only accept returns for defective products.</strong></p>
            </div>
            <ul>
                <li>Engines delivered damaged or non-functional (must be reported within 48 hours of delivery)</li>
                <li>Items that do not match the product listing (wrong part, model, or specifications)</li>
                <li>Engines that do not fit your vehicle only if compatibility was guaranteed by AutoBids</li>
                <li>Manufacturing defects discovered within the return window</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
            <h2>Non-Returnable Items</h2>
            <div class="warning-box">
                <h3>⚠️ Items That Cannot Be Returned</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Non-defective items (buyer's remorse, change of mind)</strong></li>
                    <li>Items damaged due to improper installation or handling</li>
                    <li>Products marked "as-is" or "final sale"</li>
                    <li>Installed, disassembled, or modified items</li>
                    <li>Normal wear and tear on used/refurbished engines</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
            <h2>Return Process</h2>
            <div class="process-steps">
                <ol>
                    <li><strong>Contact us</strong> at support@autobidseller.com with order number, photos, and issue description</li>
                    <li><strong>Wait for approval</strong> - Our team will confirm eligibility and provide RMA number</li>
                    <li><strong>Pack securely</strong> - RMA number must be clearly labeled on packaging</li>
                    <li><strong>Ship to provided address</strong> - Customer pays return freight unless AutoBids error</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
            <h2>Refund Timeline</h2>
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <span class="timeframe">7-10 business days</span> Refunds processed within 7-10 business days after returned item inspection
                </div>
                <div class="highlight-item">
                    <span class="timeframe">Original payment method</span> Refunds credited to original payment method used for purchase
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="policy-section">
            <h2>Cancellations</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Before shipping</strong> - Cancel without penalty before item ships</li>
                <li><strong>After shipping</strong> - Cancellation may not be possible once shipped or prepared for freight</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-box">
            <h3>📞 Contact Information</h3>
            <p>Questions about returns or refunds? Contact our support team:</p>
            <div class="contact-info">
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <strong>Email</strong>
                    support@autobidseller.com
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <strong>Phone</strong>
                    [Your Phone Number]
                </div>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <strong>Address</strong>
                    [Your Business Address]
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>